Metadata-Version: 1.0
Name: plone.memoize
Version: 1.0b2
Summary: Decorator to memoize properties bound to a request
Home-page: http://svn.plone.org/svn/plone/plone.memoize
Author: Martin Aspeli and David "Whit" Morriss
Author-email: optilude@gmx.net
License: LGPL
Description: plone.memoize provides memo decorators for Zope 3 views and regular
        classes. For views, a memo will last as long as the request, even
        if the view is looked up several times. This requires the request
        to be marked as annotatable.
        
Keywords: plone memoize decorator
Platform: UNKNOWN
